  <summary date="2020-03-31T14:06:34Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Restoring Statutory Rights and Interests of the States Act of 2019 

This bill makes written arbitration agreements in certain commercial contracts unenforceable. Specifically, such an agreement is unenforceable where an individual or a small business concern alleges, in a claim arising subsequent to the agreement,&#160;a violation of a federal or state statute or constitution.</summary>
